  "texts": [
    "The dataset is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0 Licence.",
    "Cityscapes:The Cityscape dataset [73] was provided by the R&D department of Daimler AG in co-operation with the Max Planck Institute for Informatics (MPI-IS) and the Max Planck Institute for Informatics (MPI-IS).",
    "Research and Development are in cooperation with the Max Planck Institute for Informatics (MPI-IS) and the Darmstadt Visual Reasoning Group.",
    "The Cityscape dataset focuses on the semantic understanding of urban streetscapes, and as such, it consists entirely of stereoscopic color images.",
    "The dataset has a wide diversity, including 50 different cities, different seasons (spring, summer, autumn), different weather conditions, and different scene dynamics."
  ]
